      <action-date date="20131010">October 10, 2013</action-date>
      <action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S288">Ms. Murkowski</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="S319">Mr. Begich</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S326">Mr. Udall of New Mexico</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S353">Mr. Schatz</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SLIA00">Committee on Indian Affairs</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
